abstract: Belinda Bencic beats Caroline Wozniacki in third round of BNP Paribas Open; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Belinda Bencic beat the fourth-seeded Wozniacki, 6-4, 6-4, in the BNP Paribas Open’s third round.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Tennis; Wozniacki Is Ousted
